{"tid":1822328,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班和你影食屎大架？想攪亂場革命？","createTime":"2020-01-13T01:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T02:34:44.000Z","uid":336730,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ddb4c690510cc3bb8e442acd7b056c35f57c64","tid":1822328,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英國記者海利（Johann Hari）曾在TED大會上說，葡萄牙2000年時是歐洲毒品最氾濫的國家，他們懲罰、羞辱吸毒者，但吸毒情況愈趨嚴重。他們找來醫生和科學家，決定改變對待吸毒者的方式，用那些對抗他們的經費，協助他們回到社會。葡萄牙開始協助吸毒者創業、就業，讓吸毒者「每天早上有起床的動力」。實驗至今已經過了15年，現在的葡萄牙毒物使用量下降了50％，在反毒上取得空前的成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地見到班後生仔食緊藍店，應該問下佢地係唔係冇錢食黃店？ 再和你 「請」啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請佢地食下黃店啲高質素食物 ！感化佢地"},{"pid":"efe0431c4c53d51c5b4088cb60a698232e3df5c3","tid":1822328,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"-0-0 真 失民意"},{"pid":"709a00fc059826198727298253f49f19a519cd4a","tid":1822328,"uid":221395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:00:48.000Z","msg":"幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［行動Po］一月十九 天下制裁大遊行 大家幫手推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822183</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4a9e1de1291ef82b7f56eed987e28a8cb926c93","tid":1822328,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe0431c4c53d51c5b4088cb60a698232e3df5c3","tid":1822328,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"-0-0 真 失民意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:01:26.000Z","msg":"咁你繼續破壞民意囉"},{"pid":"fe861505939021a8d27dca74e59cfaaef14ae414","tid":1822328,"uid":261